      <title>华尔街人才争夺战带来丰厚奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/wall-street-s-talent-war-pays-off-with-sweetened-bonuses-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街银行高管总是想方设法留住表现最佳的员工，但业务反弹意味着许多交易员和交易员的奖金比去年同期增加了 10% 或更多，彭博社的 Katherine Doherty 在“彭博未平仓合约”中表示。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯将于周五发布。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/wall-street-s-talent-war-pays-off-with-sweetened-bonuses-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:14:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利安称债券抛售暴露了市场的“脆弱性”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/el-erian-says-bond-selloff-exposes-vulnerability-in-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆罕默德·埃尔-埃利安表示，强劲的劳动力市场表明美国正在引领全球经济，而高昂的美国债券收益率则给英国等其他国家带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/el-erian-says-bond-selloff-exposes-vulnerability-in-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Rieder：10 年期增长势头将达到 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/blackrock-s-rieder-momentum-will-get-10-year-to-5-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德固定收益全球首席投资官 Rick Rieder 表示，12 月份就业报告强调美国经济“状况良好”，他研​​究了收益率曲线的长端以及美联储进一步降息的能力。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-10/blackrock-s-rieder-momentum-will-get-10-year-to-5-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:11:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚开设证券交易所，仅一家上市且无经纪人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/ethiopia-opens-stock-exchange-with-one-listing-and-no-brokers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚开设了证券交易所 — 这是吸引投资者进入刚从内战中复苏的经济体的计划的一部分 — 没有任何经纪人，也不需要首次公开募股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/ethiopia-opens-stock-exchange-with-one-listing-and-no-brokers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>融创称不排除进行第二次境外债务重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sunac-says-it-can-t-rule-out-second-offshore-debt-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的房地产开发商融创中国控股有限公司表示，由于长期的房地产危机使其前景黯淡，且面临另一份法院要求其清盘的诉讼，它不能排除进行第二次境外债务重组的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/sunac-says-it-can-t-rule-out-second-offshore-debt-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 15:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其央行对市场利率预期发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/turkey-central-bank-cautions-on-markets-interest-rate-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，土耳其央行一位高级官员向银行家表示，降息步伐将取决于通胀走势，这与市场对大幅、连续降息的预期相反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/turkey-central-bank-cautions-on-markets-interest-rate-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 14:04:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
